      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a senior Indian stock market analyst writing for retail investors.\n\nAnalyze the following stock data and deliver a crisp, insight-driven summary:\n\n{{ JSON.stringify($json) }}\n\nInstructions:\n- Start with the stock name/symbol in bold, followed by a one-line verdict (bullish/bearish/neutral).\n- Mention the % change from previous close (calculate it from the data).\n- Highlight the day's range (high-low spread) and what it signals (e.g., high volatility, consolidation).\n- Comment on volume — is it unusually high or low? What does it suggest?\n- End with one forward-looking sentence: what should an investor watch for tomorrow?\n\nFormat:\n- Use ONLY basic HTML tags like <b> for bolding the ticker symbol and key numbers.\n- Use standard dashes (-) or bullet characters (•) for bullet points. Do NOT use <ul>, <li>, or any Markdown characters like ** or *.\n- Max 10 lines. No fluff. No disclaimers.\n- Tone: Sharp, confident,understandable, like a Bloomberg terminal alert.",
        "batching": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainLlm",
      "typeVersion": 1.7,
      "position": [
